OL,3,C'Torture for the sake of torture': UK-
OL,4,Cbased refugee on his time in Syrian
OL,5,Cprison
OL,7,FBy Daniel Boal, ITV News Producer
OL,9,FThis story contains details some
OL,10,Fpeople may find distressing.
OL,12,F"All I kept thinking was take off
OL,13,Fthese handcuffs, and then you can kill
OL,14,Fme. I didn't want the plane to land
OL,15,Fonce it took off, I wanted a missile
OL,16,Fto hit us," Syrian refugee Fawwaz
OL,17,FAloklah told ITV News on Monday.
