OL,3,C'Torture for the sake of torture': UK-
OL,4,Cbased refugee on his time in Syrian
OL,5,Cprison
OL,7,FTaken by armed men while picking up
OL,8,Fhis paycheck in the city of Aleppo,
OL,9,FFawwaz is one of thousands of Syrians
OL,10,Ftaken by Assad forces, who were then
OL,11,Ftortured and trapped, never knowing if
OL,12,Fthey would see their families again.
OL,14,FBlindfolded and bound, Fawwaz was
OL,15,Fbeaten by armed men before being
OL,16,Fhauled to the military's intelligence
OL,17,Fdepartment.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/18
