OL,7,FThere, he spent 35 days being beaten
OL,8,Fand left unable to sleep due to
OL,9,Fhunger, before he was presented with a
OL,10,Fdocument to sign.
OL,12,F"I didn't know what was on the
OL,13,Fdocument, I just know they wanted me
OL,14,Fto say what they wanted and they were
OL,15,Fgoing to keep torturing me until I
OL,16,Fdid," he said.
OL,18,FAfter signing the document forced upon
OL,19,Fhim by his captors, Fawwaz was bundled
OL,20,Finto a small plane not knowing where
OL,21,Fhe would end up.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/18
