OL,5,Cprison
OL,7,F'We had lots of torture while they
OL,8,Fmoved us from the car to the airport.
OL,9,FThey were hitting us all the time,
OL,10,Fthey were enjoying beating us and
OL,11,Fcalling us traitors'
OL,13,FOnce on the plane, alongside others
OL,14,Fcaptured by the Assad regime, he
OL,15,Frecalls soldiers stacking other
OL,16,Fcaptives on top of one another, along
OL,17,Fwith at least two dead bodies.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/18
