OL,7,FFlown into Damascus, Fawwaz was
OL,8,Ftortured again after stepping off the
OL,9,Fplane, still unaware of what the Assad
OL,10,Fregime had accused him of.
OL,12,FThere was one female captive among the
OL,13,F51 men - she was violently assaulted
OL,14,Fand mistreated in front of them.
OL,16,FTaken to another department in the
OL,17,Fcapital, he was cast into a room,
OL,18,Falready filled with other people.
OL,20,F"I was told I no longer have a name, I
OL,21,Fhave a number," he said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/18
