OL,7,F"The room was five and a half metres
OL,8,Flong and maybe three and a half metres
OL,9,Flong. Each of us had a tile, it was
OL,10,Fmaybe 30cm by 30cm, on this we could
OL,11,Fonly sit or stand. I did not have a
OL,12,Ftile for the first two days."
OL,14,FFor the next five months and 10 days,
OL,15,FFawwaz shared this room with 86 people.
OL,17,FAt least 25 people died while they
OL,18,Fwere locked in the room with Fawwaz.
OL,19,FTheir bodies were taken out of the
OL,20,Froom, and their place was filled with
OL,21,Fnew captives.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/18
