OL,7,F"The room was five and a half metres
OL,8,Flong and maybe three and a half metres
OL,9,Flong. The problem is that you are
OL,10,Funable to sleep because the space is
OL,11,Ftoo crowded," Fawwaz said
OL,13,F"My biggest dream at that time was to
OL,14,Fbe able to lay down. I dreamt that I
OL,15,Fwas in a room alone," Fawwaz said,
OL,16,F"this is the only dream that I had for
OL,17,Fthe entire time. I just dreamt of
OL,18,Fsomewhere that I could sleep.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/18
