OL,7,FHe added: "In the Palestine department
OL,8,F- that is what they called it - they
OL,9,Ftortured us many times. Torture for
OL,10,Fthe sake of torture. They would drag
OL,11,Fus out into the cold and throw
OL,12,Ffreezing water over us. Then they
OL,13,Fwould beat us with pipes.
OL,15,F"They would wait for the pipe wounds
OL,16,Fto heal on our backs before they did
OL,17,Fit again.
