OL,7,F"In those five months I saw many
OL,8,Fpeople die," he said, adding that he
OL,9,Fsaw their corpses being thrown into
OL,10,Fthe toilets.
OL,12,FOver the weekend more than 50 years of
OL,13,FAssad rule in Syria crumbled after
OL,14,Frebels took the capital Damascus,
OL,15,Fforcing President Bashar al-Assad to
OL,16,Fflee to Moscow.
