OL,7,FPeaceful anti-government protests in
OL,8,F2011 were met with violence and
OL,9,Fspilled out into a 14-year long civil
OL,10,Fwar - one that has left more than half
OL,11,Fa million people dead, and half of
OL,12,FSyria's 23 million pre-war population
OL,13,Fdisplaced.
OL,15,FAmong those still left scarred by the
OL,16,Fconflict are the people who were taken
OL,17,Fand tortured by Assad's forces.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/18
