OL,7,FUsed as a tool for repression,
OL,8,Fthousands of families still bear the
OL,9,Fpsychological toll of not knowing
OL,10,Fwhere their loved ones are.
OL,12,FAfter five months trapped on his 30cm
OL,13,Fby 30cm tile, Fawwaz had his number
OL,14,Fcalled by the guards.
OL,16,F"I knew I was leaving, I just didn't
OL,17,Fknow where. I wasn't sure if I was
OL,18,Fgoing to be killed.," he said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/18
