OL,7,FMoved to a military police facility,
OL,8,FFawwaz was finally able to lie down
OL,9,Ffor the first time in over five months.
OL,11,FHe was then transferred to Adra
OL,12,FCentral Prison, where, he says,
OL,13,Feveryone was branded a "terrorist".
OL,15,FAfter meeting someone in the prison
OL,16,Fwho knew where his family was from, he
OL,17,Fwas able to get a message to his
OL,18,Ffather.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/18
