OL,7,FAfter raising around $1,000 (#785),
OL,8,FFawwaz's father was able to pay for a
OL,9,Fsolicitor and his son was able to get
OL,10,Fa date in court where he was cleared
OL,11,Fof terrorism charges.
OL,13,FHowever, after thinking that he was
OL,14,Fgoing to be freed, he was then picked
OL,15,Fup by another military department
OL,16,Fwhere he was informed he was guilty of
OL,17,Fother crimes against the Syrian
OL,18,Fgovernment.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/18
