OL,7,FForced to bribe the police holding
OL,8,Fhim, he was eventually freed after
OL,9,Fnine months in captivity and was
OL,10,Ffinally able to see his family.
OL,12,FUpon returning home, the father of
OL,13,Ffour was told by ISIS, who had taken
OL,14,Fover his village, that he would be
OL,15,Funable to return to teaching.
OL,17,FIn order to make money for his family,
OL,18,Fhe was forced to become a porter.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/18
