OL,3,C'Torture for the sake of torture': UK-
OL,4,Cbased refugee on his time in Syrian
OL,5,Cprison
OL,7,FWith conflict still raging in Syria,
OL,8,Fand traumatised by his months in
OL,9,Fcaptivity, Fawwaz was smuggled into
OL,10,FTurkey in 2019. He had been left with
OL,11,Fno legal route to secure his family
OL,12,Fsafe passage into Turkey.
OL,14,FEventually, he and his family were
OL,15,Fable to secure asylum in the UK. While
OL,16,Fthey are currently being housed in
OL,17,Ftemporary accommodation, Fawwaz says
OL,18,Fhe is "happy to know that his family
OL,19,Fare safe".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/18
