OL,7,F"Everything is okay here, yes if we
OL,8,Fhad a house it would be perfect, but I
OL,9,Flove this country. It is somewhere we
OL,10,Fcan be safe," he added.
OL,12,F"I wish my country would be a safe
OL,13,Fcountry for all Syrians, irrespective
OL,14,Fof what they believe or to whom they
OL,15,Fbelong. At the end of the day we are
OL,16,Fall Syrian.
OL,18,F"What I want is accountability for the
OL,19,Fpeople who are responsible for what
OL,20,Fhappened and bring them to justice."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G17/18
